==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Photo-engraving
<hw>Pho`to-en*grav"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Photo-</ets> + <ets>engraving</ets>.]</ety> <def>The process
of obtaining an etched or engraved plate from the photographic image, to
be used in printing; also, a picture produced by such a
process.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Photo-engrave</ent>⟦br⟧
